Package org.pdp.game

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDungeon
    Represents the different mazes that a player can traverse through.
    IDungeonReadOnly
    This represents a read only interface which is supplied to the interface.
    ILocation
    Represents a location in the dungeon.
    IPlayer
    Represents different types of players who can travel through the dungeon.
    Monster
    Represents monsters that can be present in the dungeon.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Arrowtracer
    A class which traces the path of the arrow.
    Dungeon
    Represents a dungeon which a player will traverse collecting treasures on the way.
    Dungeon.DungeonBuilder
    This is a class responsible for building our dungeon.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Direction
    An enum that represents the four cardinal directions.
    Smell
    The Intensity of smell at a location based on monster proximity.
    Treasures
    The different treasures present in the dungeon.
    Weapon
    The weapons that will be available for use in the dungeon.
